1. *"Oni su otišli u šerife da prijave krađu." (They went to the sheriff to report the theft.)
2. *"Šerife su zaustavili zločinca." (The sheriffs stopped the criminal.)
3. *"Šerifu je pozvala policija." (The sheriff was called by the police.)
4. *"Šerifi su proveravali dokaze." (The sheriffs were checking the evidence.)
5. *"Šerifovi se trenutno bore sa zločinom." (The sheriffs are currently fighting crime.)